[VS2-333] Data Collection sources

Background:
TBC

User Story:
As a Data Owner/Delegate Data Owner, I want to specify data sources for each Data Collection so that data sourcing and access are clearly defined.

Acceptance criteria:
GIVEN defined data modality for a Study WHEN the source system for it is recorded THEN selection of data source for each data modality is enabled.
GIVEN defined data modality for a Study WHEN it is submitted for execution THEN no blank data source for each modality is present.